      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Al Hassan Bin Mahboub, from Ali Bin Raib, from Ibn Abu Yafour, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The patience is the head of the <span class=\"iTxt\">Emān</span>’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "1. A number of our people have narrated from Sahl ibn Ziyad from al-Hassan ibn Mahbub from Ali ibn Ri’ab from ibn abu Ya’fur from abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) has said, ‘Patience is the head of belief.” "
        ]
      }
